1128
00:56:03,956 --> 00:56:05,488
Okey, lebih baik awak...

1129
00:56:05,490 --> 00:56:07,456
Yeah?

1130
00:56:07,458 --> 00:56:09,126
Hei, saya ada bercakap
dengan beberapa pegawai lain,

1131
00:56:09,128 --> 00:56:11,361
