00:56:53,105 --> 00:56:54,938
- Yeah!
- <i>Helo? Awak tak apa-apa?</i>

1156
00:56:54,940 --> 00:56:55,906
<i>Laurel?</i>

1157
00:56:55,908 --> 00:56:58,375
Oh, Colt, saya tak boleh bercakap.
Budak-budak itu perlukan saya.

1158
00:56:58,377 --> 00:57:00,243
Nanti!

1159
00:57:00,245 --> 00:57:01,914
Tak guna budak-budak tu.

1160
00:57:06,318 --> 00:57:07,518
Huh.

1161
00:57:34,013 --> 00:57:35,879
<i>♪ Kami dalam suatu pencarian</i>

1162
00:57:35,881 --> 00:57:37,614
<i>♪ Ayah kami, kami
