1242
01:02:11,223 --> 01:02:14,192
Oh, waktu dah separuh jalan.

1243
01:02:14,694 --> 01:02:16,826
Aku perlukan tali tu tadi.

1244
01:02:16,828 --> 01:02:19,197
Oh, tapi kau perlukan
ke tadi?

1245
