lelaki ibu kita.

1282
01:04:14,079 --> 01:04:16,214
Okey, sekarang kau lari
dari polis.

1283
01:04:27,794 --> 01:04:29,259
Bertahan!

1284
01:04:29,261 --> 01:04:31,363
Whoa!

1285
01:04:34,801 --> 01:04:37,333
Yeah! Bagus, Guinevere!

1286
01:04:53,151 --> 01:04:55,485
